{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had the pleasure to go and shot 200 or 300 just-- just for fun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And happened me, I was-- I didn't know, like I said before, to push him this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was there, And I was-- and I hold his-- his ear of the guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told him, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] after the guy to look in front of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bang, they shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got scared, and I left him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't push him, any he go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time was not this Holland guy from the SS, was somebody else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Soon as the dead body fell in the back, from the blood spill of his head, he dirty his boots with blood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And right away, got the shot gun to shoot me because the blood fell on his boot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And thank God that my brother was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my brother he has some acquaintance with this guy because always my brother was there holding the ear.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody else could do that, that thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And thank God he said, oh, my brother, my brother, my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is the only way he didn't shot me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And right away, the other guy with the hose, he went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We cleaned the-- the German boot, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was the first and the last time I was in that place holding the ear from somebody else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When that thing was coming, I was hiding, getting away much as I could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I never went back again to see the-- to see those thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Holland, SS from Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never told us names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why they should ask our names?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have no names either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had the numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Put them in the elevator.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They come upstairs with the oven.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
